Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:05.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Some time ago, the Brown War raged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:11.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong winds were blowing in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? Will this never end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we win? Are we defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.\NBy the way, against whom are we fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:37.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If we knew that, what would it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And how are we going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:43.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:47.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto-san, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. She'll be fine.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:59.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.27,0:01:00.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?\NThat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:10.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why?\NBecause...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:12.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?\NBecause Kyuuto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Yeah, Ok...let's pay attention again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, those kinds of interruption happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:32.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he continued to write poems, even though he was aware he was dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't got your career sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:41.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Career sheet?\NRight, your career sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:45.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something far more important going on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!\NSomething more important than your career?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even under torture I can't tell!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What next stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing, of course.\NIt's kissing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NHow far have you guys gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"You guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:25.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean.. you and Kyuuto...\NHow far have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!! Perhaps you went straight to Level 4!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Isn't it so? You did it with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... You went right in...\NWow! Right in? Right in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:39.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no next level.\NKyuuto is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:48.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far we go, we can't unite with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we follow the God of Heaven and Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakugo? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've been told that the way I talk is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying by listening to rakugo (comic stories).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:17.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your way of speaking is getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:21.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, your career sheet? What do you mean by "Making Efforts"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...\N"Young Master"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:30.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I... nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the God of Heaven and Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think he will watch over you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, when the grain of rice does not make an effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:46.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the God of Heaven and Earth will not watch over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... just a minute, ok? It seems really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:59.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,even Kyuuto has something like a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:08.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that she is trying really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:14.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off and show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off and show me!\NHey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:06.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Nakao?!\NYou're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!\NOw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't act like a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:21.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto-san... You've touched her before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have, right?\NWell, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"How"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ... I mean....\NI knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't human, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's human!\NCan't you see? She's human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides... It's not like we were holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the evidence if you have any!\NWhat do you mean, "evidence"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying, "She's human."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:13.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like crying...\NShe probably cries a lot. She's a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she cries a lot! She's a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make Ogawa-sensei cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean Kyuuto.\NWhy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao said that she's a robot. He seems to suspect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:30.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And if she cries, then he'll believe she's a human?\NShe can't cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically speaking, I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be very difficult to make her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears are ready for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You can cry?\NPuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... cry! Can you cry now?\NOk. I'll ask Nakao to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:55.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, without a reason it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,First you have to say something to make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to make you cry?\NQuick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do that. I might hurt her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:12.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kyuuto is a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Some sort of insult should come to your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:22.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, please say it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Well, don't be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!\NI can't say it! I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:51.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man! I want to become a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of all the things we're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:58.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to charge ahead.\NIs that the power of the beast, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Love beast."\NWow... What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:12.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Love" and "Beast".\NOn the other side of that door...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think does happen there?!\NI guess
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,this sort of thing,\Nand that sort of thing, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:22.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a picture!\NWhat an amazing store!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, someone went in. That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty brazen to go there in the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:37.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!\NShow me! Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daa!\NHey, it's pretty good, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You got it enlarged?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:05.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's the first time we're in a photo together with a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in it, am I?\NWell, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're the one who took the picture.\NRight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:16.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But imagine, even you were properly added to the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:20.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding. I'm there? Where, where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the lion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow this resembles our family, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does. Absolutely fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to send this to Grandpa too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way is fine.\NOh! Oh! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:51.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,An unemployed, homeless man was arrested. The suspect said, "Anyone would have been fine"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anyone would have been fine", you say. No way! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying, "Me, Me", don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And you keep whining about everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't going to work with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think anyone would be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait.. Don't cut me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:17.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you even recognise your own son's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen to a person till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:44.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you I can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's certainly not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come with me for a moment?\NNo, no, that won't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Only for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:06.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it should be about 3 cm to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:12.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Yes, yes.\NPlease don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NWhen you are sitting there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,my computer runs smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the reason for that?\NI have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:35.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm pretty busy, so...\NYou can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:39.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...  You don't really need me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I've made several tests. I'm a scientist, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:47.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But unless you are here, it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:52.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I end up getting a job transfer, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get married, I'll bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Y.. you mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't written anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:18.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my career sheet?\NWhatever. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:22.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to chose between things that do not interest me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and things I'm not capable to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been seriously thinking about these options but I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:34.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no job waiting only for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:38.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway. For me, anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well ... Well ... Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai did say something to her.\NI wonder what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably awful things.\NWhat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:16.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she should be treated like a human.\N"Treated"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:21.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Like embracing and stroking her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I should do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You made her cry, didn't you?\NWhat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:29.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Do it!\NHere??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a love beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:03.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,decided to go to the same university as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:10.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that. But you have a higher ranking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:13.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can choose to go wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not at the same university, there's no meaning for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't take responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... No... well... But, given my nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:27.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I could go to a good university, I might not go, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:31.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:35.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but... um....\NAm I a burden to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:37.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:41.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I am a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?\NStill nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he wipe her tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:04.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't make such a pretty girl cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:14.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you stop crying because of what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be! It can't be! Eh...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be. You're lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it hadn't to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how I have been configured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I modify the settings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?\NI'm not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pure human, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:46.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go?\NWhereever you want, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:25.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is dad going to that store?\NDon't you think that's disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:29.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take-chan is working there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Working there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:35.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop him?\NSee, it's the "Love Beast"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:43.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Our financial situation isn't good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my hospital bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not just that. Other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to get a part-time job,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm bad at such things, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:00.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Take-chan said, "It's alright. I'll do something myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:03.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...there are probably other jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why "Love Beast"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's a place where one's appearance does not matter", Take-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect important things,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,amazingly he never gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God, you weren't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:27.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when everything had fallen to pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,he came to pick up the small fragments,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:38.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,struggling to put back things the way they were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:54.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:19:00.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm uneasy about his job at "Love Beast",
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:03.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to believe in Take-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! Why did you cry yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master did it violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NYoung Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it violently? You!?\NHow indecent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!\NI'm telling the truth... I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:43.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master has absolutely no understanding of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say, "Anything would be fine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You really said, "Anything would be fine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:55.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think! That's not it!\NEh? Why are you thinking that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:03.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't this person with beauty and brains write decently?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:07.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, no one says "beauty and brains" any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:11.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's "science combination"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Science combination"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful woman who's good at science.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let us drink this thick syrup."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Nakahara Chuuya poem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also good at literature. Do you want to drink something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Make it cool and drink it through thick straws."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:46.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Without glancing aside let us drink gently."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mozuku (seaweed) soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:21:03.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's nothing more that I would ask."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:14.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:17.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My career.\NI'll proceed to engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not doing good in mathematics at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'm going to focus more on math!\NI'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this, all of a sudden?\NWhy don't you try arts and literature?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Literature is no use!\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to construct robots!\NRobots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:37.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will construct a robot that can cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:42.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. You know, it's already November....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:46.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't become what they're able to become,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:49.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,they become what they want to become.\NAm I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am tortured, I won't change my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:58.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:13.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,where students who can't decide on their careers are detained?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a nobody. I'm Fujino Tsukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:22.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I thought you had a darker aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't make up your mind about your career, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:30.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For your information, I have already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:32.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NWait a minute, show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:41.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NIt's ok, we have about the same rank in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Something this difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of reasons.\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:52.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:57.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:03.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:06.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to decide what you want to do with your life today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:12.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have neither the courage to write something down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,nor the courage to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei, I made a great discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:38.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The computer also works with a rubber tree. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:43.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't come anymore, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:46.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ... A rubber tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:24:02.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"My life that day was like an empty chair."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:08.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, then.\NSee you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:13.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, bye!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:15.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat ramen afterwards...\NRamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.87,0:24:27.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not wearing it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:30.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wear it in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:32.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a medical check-up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:35.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm visiting a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.47,0:24:43.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.38,0:24:46.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Just leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:48.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it?\NBut you have to submit this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:53.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok. Whatever I write will just be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.89,0:24:55.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:25:00.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:04.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write that. There's no way I can write something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.86,0:25:06.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.88,0:25:11.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Our homeroom teacher would get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.89,0:25:15.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't think of anything else I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.17,0:25:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't write anything adequate enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:24.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But can't you express your true feelings somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.87,0:25:36.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impatient, I'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.36,0:25:40.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what will happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.87,0:25:44.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to express openly what I am thinking, but
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.37,0:25:46.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more troubled if I say those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.47,0:25:56.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say things like "I'm alright" not just to comfort someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:26:02.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to say "Thank you. I'll try my best".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.89,0:26:06.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your teacher won't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:09.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, say it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.36,0:26:11.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.47,0:26:18.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To sing about such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:20.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:29.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you going to play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.88,0:26:31.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.38,0:26:35.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come with you?\NAre you allowed to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.95,0:26:39.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright if I drive by taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.37,0:26:42.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ok with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.44,0:27:00.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The patients are waiting.\NGo! Hurry hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:01.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.88,0:27:06.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. I'll go.\NCan somebody go to Ishida-san, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.37,0:27:09.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.\NBe careful. He's nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.37,0:27:12.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong-flavored diet is not good for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.36,0:27:14.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The prescribed painkiller doesn't have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.88,0:27:17.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.\NI'm here for a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.43,0:27:19.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:34.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.88,0:27:38.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's right.\NWhat about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.96,0:27:48.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why can't anyone understand the truth?",
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.88,0:27:52.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,you said, but
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.86,0:27:55.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that's probably not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.89,0:27:59.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.37,0:28:03.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,there are people who are seriously thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.91,0:28:05.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.86,0:28:11.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who are working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.37,0:28:15.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here is thinking about and working solely for the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.87,0:28:20.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they are all mature adults, they are warm-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.36,0:28:24.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of those hard-working people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.41,0:28:26.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,you can say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.37,0:28:32.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you betray their trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.37,0:28:38.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:40.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.37,0:28:54.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. This looks like a Japanese wordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.39,0:28:57.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.38,0:29:00.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.90,0:29:08.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I wan't to talk to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:12.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Luna-chan's collectibles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.38,0:29:15.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Luna-chan's collectibles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.88,0:29:19.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, young boy right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.37,0:29:23.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to sell with such a low voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.39,0:29:29.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I'll help you selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.88,0:29:38.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good~
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.87,0:29:41.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although made poorly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.87,0:29:44.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.98,0:29:55.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These two you will sell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:57.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With a loud voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.37,0:30:13.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.92,0:30:16.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home. Ryuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.86,0:30:22.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.\NWhat have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:24.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.57,0:30:28.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just asking what's with your career sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.89,0:30:33.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's with it"?\NI can't graduate anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.39,0:30:36.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.\NI don't care whether I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.36,0:30:40.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:45.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been? It's already late.\NHow about you? You always come home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.57,0:30:51.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, seems like your father and mother are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.88,0:30:54.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?\NOur principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.46,0:30:58.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming home anymore recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.87,0:31:00.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.35,0:31:04.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They got divorced.\NDivorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:10.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you eat curry?\NI've cooked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.88,0:31:13.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.90,0:31:17.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all the way here, but I still don't know what to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.47,0:31:20.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:22.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.86,0:31:26.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,when will you make a decision?\NYou're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.86,0:31:31.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.38,0:31:34.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt the girl I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:37.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected her of double-dating with a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.44,0:31:42.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After we had broken up, I ate bread with bean jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.36,0:31:45.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from a poor family,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.86,0:31:49.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was the best bread I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.38,0:31:52.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sweet and fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.39,0:31:56.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It kept me thinking "So, there is something this good in the world".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.88,0:32:00.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised myself to take back my accusations
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:06.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and bought that bread for her,\Nbut when I reached her home,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.37,0:32:11.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she had died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.36,0:32:19.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, when I came back to the place that sells the bread, I bought lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.88,0:32:22.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.43,0:32:25.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.37,0:32:27.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.86,0:32:36.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had known she'll die, I could have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:44.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, say something like "I'll do what I can".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.37,0:32:47.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then think of something that you can do and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.88,0:32:49.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.88,0:32:52.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,First, before your mom and dad come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.88,0:32:55.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,clean up this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.39,0:33:00.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash the glasses until they shine brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.42,0:33:04.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash the dirty clothes and fold them neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.89,0:33:08.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With a smiling face say "Welcome home" when they come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.36,0:33:11.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.88,0:33:15.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,serve them a warm meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.37,0:33:20.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing...\NJust do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.43,0:33:24.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By such things people's hearts are won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.86,0:33:26.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.93,0:33:46.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother wrote this with a lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.56,0:34:18.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! I'm finished!\NI think I'm going blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.57,0:34:21.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't decide on what to do. I'll be doomed in eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.57,0:34:24.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.57,0:34:30.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no forever in this world.\NEven the universe will have an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.70,0:34:33.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The universe will have an end?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:37.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The universe consists of 23% dark matter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:40.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and 73% invisible energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.04,0:34:42.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So most of it is invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.56,0:34:47.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All other substances are only 4%.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.56,0:34:53.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, as time progresses, energy keeps on increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.08,0:34:56.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? How does it increase?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.15,0:34:59.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Matter is falling apart.\NFalling apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.54,0:35:04.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All atoms are falling apart until\Nthey turn into small particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.05,0:35:07.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Small particles...what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.55,0:35:10.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.55,0:35:12.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the blackboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.55,0:35:14.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.57,0:35:17.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the corridor, the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.12,0:35:20.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the lawn, the athletic field,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.06,0:35:23.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the flowers, the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.57,0:35:28.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.55,0:35:32.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, the quantity of energy is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:36.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happens.\NThere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.63,0:35:39.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The energy keeps on increasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.05,0:35:42.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,even if this is beyond our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.05,0:35:46.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The atoms fall apart\Nuntil only small particles are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.04,0:35:51.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the darkness keeps on increasing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.06,0:35:54.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,until the Earth is dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.61,0:35:59.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that happens, the Sun will have collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.53,0:36:01.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun also?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.55,0:36:05.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the Sun will also vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.06,0:36:07.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.56,0:36:13.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it will happen in 100 billion years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.06,0:36:26.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This theory will be confirmed in year 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.06,0:36:32.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In year 2025, the word "eternity" will be erased from the national language textbooks
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.03,0:36:36.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.59,0:36:40.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't use the word "eternity" any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.54,0:36:43.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:45.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.55,0:36:54.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.07,0:37:08.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh! What happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.57,0:37:11.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nurse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.54,0:37:13.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become a nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.56,0:37:17.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the name of our rock group.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.58,0:37:20.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see ... Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:23.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be a rocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.07,0:37:24.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.54,0:37:28.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:32.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Man~ you as a rocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:39.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it can't be helped. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.62,0:37:43.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a friend who works in that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.04,0:37:45.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try asking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.56,0:37:50.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.54,0:37:54.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:57.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.05,0:38:01.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I didn't take serious then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.04,0:38:10.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"People don't become what they're able to become,"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:14.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"they become what they want to become."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.07,0:38:17.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.54,0:38:19.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.65,0:38:28.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.55,0:38:32.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know "maneyozu"?\NThat's a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.04,0:38:35.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no eternity in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.04,0:38:37.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the universe will have an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.04,0:38:43.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All atoms are torn apart into tiny particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.12,0:38:49.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.04,0:38:58.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.05,0:39:01.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The universe will have an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.12,0:39:02.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.63,0:39:09.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in here will be torn into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.54,0:39:12.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.55,0:39:21.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?\NHey! The meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.05,0:39:36.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.53,0:39:41.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy's peak was at 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.04,0:39:44.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No no... later it get's worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.54,0:39:50.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.61,0:39:53.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kyuuto?\NShe went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.03,0:39:56.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wants to watch a rakugo and learn from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.55,0:39:59.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that play "The Pumpkin Shop"?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.04,0:40:03.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When she meets Young Master again, she wants to be able to talk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.54,0:40:06.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.55,0:40:23.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.55,0:40:25.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.06,0:40:33.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.57,0:40:36.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of the rice paddies will apparently disappear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.63,0:40:40.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And not only the God of the rice paddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.05,0:40:43.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,everything will disappear when the Earth turns to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.05,0:40:49.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it completely, but me and you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.06,0:40:53.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,are just like the other 4% of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.04,0:40:56.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.05,0:41:02.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called dark energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.55,0:41:04.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.57,0:41:07.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.54,0:41:13.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.65,0:41:18.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,think that "anything is fine" and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.57,0:41:22.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.56,0:41:26.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,While we
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.06,0:41:30.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,keep on saying "anyhow" and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.05,0:41:33.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the darkness keeps growing bigger and bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.12,0:41:39.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and the universe is gradually torn to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.06,0:41:47.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we should root our most important things
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.06,0:41:51.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,deep in our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.05,0:41:55.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,so that they can't be easily dispersed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.07,0:41:59.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing them tightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.04,0:42:03.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:09.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that eventually they will disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.05,0:42:11.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll strive harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.07,0:42:17.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:25.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,do you have something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.05,0:42:31.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.56,0:42:37.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never say something like "anything is fine".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.04,0:42:48.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.05,0:42:55.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,embracing my 4% of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.07,0:43:17.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\NShe hasn't come home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.04,0:43:21.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok. I'll come visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.06,0:43:24.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we neighbours?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.06,0:43:38.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you serve rice here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.54,0:43:41.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have yaki-udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.04,0:43:44.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ok.\NThen... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.55,0:43:51.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I have decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.12,0:43:59.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This important 4% part that I embraced,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:01.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,from now on, I'll live for it.
